    {
        "content": "<p>surajk-m <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13076#issuecomment-4468550600\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13076\">issue #13076</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Hey @alexcrichton, please review the PR.</p>\n<p>While looking into this, I also noticed that <code>AtomicCas</code> has the same shape for sub-word types. Specifically, the <code>// reload value to t0.</code> block in the <code>ty.bits() &lt; 32</code> path issues a second <code>lr.w.aqrl</code> before <code>AtomicOP::merge</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">store_value</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ty</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">bits</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">32</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"c1\">// reload value to t0.</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">Inst</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Atomic</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">op</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">AtomicOP</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">load_op</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ty</span><span class=\"p\">),</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">// second lr.w.aqrl</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">rd</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">t0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">addr</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">zero_reg</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">amo</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">AMO</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">SeqCst</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">emit</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">sink</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">emit_info</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">state</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">AtomicOP</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">merge</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">t0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">writable_spilltmp_reg</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">offset</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ty</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 595542326,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1778975051
    },
